snippet.title: [PS2 Longplay] .hack//MUTATION Part 1
snippet.description: Just like I said, it's time to continue on with .Hacks' story. Other than going through the intro and some story missions, I also complete two missions that gets me two new partners. Plus I obtained a Snakey Grunty. Small side not, but I'm aware that the audio lags a little bit in the video, but I can't help it. I actually tried recording this before and I ended up with the lag still. But it shouldn't stick around in the other parts. I should get a video up tomorrow. Until then, subscribe and Enjoy!!
